<i>something that is plucked
from the wild.</i>

32:28.113 --> 32:31.515
<i>Once the snakes are in, that
should be really, just, you know,</i>

32:31.517 --> 32:33.116
<i>the ribbon on top.</i>

32:34.552 --> 32:35.986
[Sara] Come on good girl.

32:38.256 --> 32:39.756
Do you want all that?

32:40.058 --> 32:44.594
Polly Kangaroo, come on. You know
I'm serious when I use your full name.

32:50.268 --> 32:52.135
- Look!
- Wow!

32:58.343 --> 32:59.810
I think that looks pretty good.

32:59.812 --> 33:02.245
- Yeah, I think it came out really nice.
- [Don] Yeah.

33:02.247 --> 33:05.916
I love how the plants, they
blended that, as good as they could.

33:05.918 --> 33:07.451
Pool will be nice.

33:07.453 --> 33:10.153
In their habitat there's a lot of little
streams and stuff that go through it.

33:10.155 --> 33:11.855
So, that'll be good.

33:11.857 --> 33:15.258
<i>The Mang vipers came to us
from a confiscation</i>

33:15.260 --> 33:16.994
<i>the New York authorities
carried out.</i>

33:16.996 --> 33:22.933
And a lot of the animals in that
confiscation had a viral disease problem.

33:22.935 --> 33:26.870
<i>But others, we were able
to successfully clear.</i>

33:26.872 --> 33:30.007
<i>So it's gratifying that some of
